.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-SPENDABLE-STDDEV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-spendable-stddev \- FEAT-2830 channel-spendable-stddev
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-spendable-stddev
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes standard deviation of spendable_msat across peer channels (FEAT-2830).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.TP
.B spendable_stddev_msat
Population standard deviation of spendable_msat values across channels.
.TP
.B n
Number of data points used.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
